**Example 1: 删除文件夹**

编排空间-删除文件夹

Input: 

```
tccli wedata DeleteDsFolder --cli-unfold-argument  \
    --ProjectId 1460947878944567296 \
    --FolderId d1962251-b6b9-4b9f-9039-e6456697cecf
```

Output: 
```
{
    "Response": {
        "Data": true,
        "RequestId": "d1962251-b6b9-4b9f-9039-e6456697cecf"
    }
}
```
